text: National Highway 330D, commonly referred to as NH 330D is a national highway in India. It is a secondary route of National Highway 30. NH-330D runs in the state of Uttar Pradesh in India. == Route == NH330D connects Sitapur, Misrikh, Pratap Nagar, Hardoi, Bilgram and Kannauj in the state of Uttar Pradesh. == Junctions == : Terminal near Sitapur. : near Hardoi : Terminal near Kannauj. == See also == * List of National Highways in India * List of National Highways in India by state == References == == External links == * NH 330D on OpenStreetMap Category:National highways in India Category:National Highways in Uttar Pradesh
